title: Dark Vador - Tom Tom GPS Voice (but Garmin guide)
description:
Everything is in the title: french voice of Dark Vador, for Tom Tom GPS.

I was fucked up when I saw that the Garmin voice I ordered was for Tom Tom... It is a Tom Tom voice. The given guide is for Garmin voices.

To install the voice, just copy darkV.vif and data99.chk into the Voice folder of your Tom Tom GPS.

I hope you will be happy to have it! Take this advantage^^
